Data Exchange / Invariant Credit

Data Structures v1.0

⸻

1. Core design principle

There are really only five layers:
	1.	Identity
	2.	Raw signal
	3.	Processed signal
	4.	Contribution / credit
	5.	Market / payout

Everything should map cleanly into one of those.

⸻

