14. Deep invariant

The most important thing structurally is this:

RawDataEvent -> SignalUnit -> ContributionRecord -> InvariantCredit -> UserPayout

That is your canonical chain.

Or in words:

observation becomes signal
signal becomes contribution
contribution becomes portable credit
credit becomes economic reward

That chain is the whole engine.

